Nov 30 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Coca Cola HBC, Flutter Entertainment and Iberdrola, on Tuesday.


HIGHLIGHTS


* Coca Cola HBC CCH.L: JP Morgan raises to overweight from neutral

* Compagnie Des Alpes SA CDAF.PA: Societe Generale raises to hold from sell

* Flutter Entertainment Plc FLTRF.I: CFRA raises to strong buy from buy

* Iberdrola IBE.MC: RBC raises to outperform from sector perform

* Kion Group AG KGX.DE: Societe Generale raises to buy from hold
